- ESSD:

  - PL0: 1 to 2048.

  - PL1: 20 to 2048.

  - PL2: 461 to 2048.

  - PL3: 1261 to 2048.

- ESSD AutoPL disk: 1 to 2048.

- Other disk categories: 20 to 2048.

The value of this parameter must be greater than or equal to max{1, ImageSize}.

Default value: max{40, ImageSize}.', example='100'),
