Default value: false.', example='false'),
  azBalance?: boolean(name='AzBalance', description='Specifies whether to evenly distribute the capacity of the scaling group across multiple availability zones. This parameter is valid only when `MultiAZPolicy` is set to `COMPOSABLE`. Valid values:

