    compensateWithOnDemand?: boolean(name='CompensateWithOnDemand', description='When `MultiAZPolicy` is set to `COST_OPTIMIZED`, this parameter specifies whether to automatically create on-demand instances to meet capacity requirements when spot instances are unavailable due to price or inventory. Valid values:

